Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Here's your chance to own a piece of paradise that generates income. This multi-cabin resort property boasts a wide array of outdoor activities on the waterfront with onsite amenities to keep guests coming back for more. With 12 cabins to rent out and covid-19 pushing people to pay premiums for cottage vacations, now is the time to take advantage of this unique opportunity to own a waterfront resort property on a secluded lake. The combined total size of all structures including all cabins and the main house is 7414 sq. ft.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Live The Beach Life! Lakefront Views From The Comfort Of Your Own Home. This Luxurious 1,465 Sq. Ft. Condo Features 3 Bedrooms, 1.5 Bath, 1 Car Garage And Breath-Taking Views Of Lake Ontario. Located Less Than A 5 Minute Drive To The Qew. Direct Access To The Waterfront Trial; An 8 Km Paved Shoreline Trail. Within Close Proximity To Lakeshore Road Amenities.

****Property must be sold with 52 Laurel Street**** Two income producing properties located in Uptown Waterloo close to all the amenities. Units are always leased with long term tenant's. Potential for redevelopment in the future. Gross Income Is $67,200.00 between both properties. Great opportunity for smaller investor to enter the market with little to no risk.

Opportunity to acquire a 3 building portfolio located on a prominent corner in the centre of downtown Stratford. The portfolio totals 68,133 Sq. Ft. of Gross Floor Area comprised of 59,891 Sq. Ft. commercial and 8,242 Sq. Ft. residential with a total of 63 parking stalls. The residential component of the offering consists of 10 newly built-out rental apartments. The commercial component of the portfolio consists of a total of 53,725 Sq. Ft. of rentable area, including 41,898 Sq. Ft.  or 78% - that is leased on a long term basis to Scotiabank.

Constructed in 2014, highly desired purpose built apartment in Timmins. 34 large suites in 24 one-bedroom and 10 two-bedroom units. Solid concrete construction with high insulation values ensuring energy efficiency. On-site laundry, storage, and social common room among the amenities. Building also has an elevator and is monitored 24 hours through a security system. Each unit is well appointed and has its own climate control including A/C.
